casebody.data:
No. 118,

Misc.

DuBois v. Mossey et al.

C. A. 7th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas would grant certiorari and reverse this *870judgment on the ground that petitioner has been denied a trial by jury which the Seventh Amendment to the Constitution is intended to guarantee. Walter L. Clements for petitioner. Charles C. Collins for the State Mutual Farm Ins. Co., respondent.
